com.diagnal.engage.campaign

Class EngageCampaign

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.diagnal.engage.campaign.EngageCampaign

  • public class EngageCampaign
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a Campaign from Engage.
    Data associated with a campaign be access by implementing CampaignTriggerListener and registering with Engage.setCampaignTriggerListener(CampaignTriggerListener)
